<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink374">
<l>pallūḻ niṉaippiṉu nalleṉ ṟūḻa</l>
<l>mīḷi muṉpiṟ kāḷai kāppa</l>
<l>muṭiyakam pukāak kūntalaḷ</l>
<l>kaṭuvaṉu maṟiyāk kāṭiṟan tōḷē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though I thought about her all the time,  </l>
<l>the girl whose tresses don’t enter the knot, </l>
<l>traversed the wilderness of intense sunshine </l>
<l>unknown even to male monkeys, </l>
<l>before and behind protected by her young man, </l>
<l>who is stronger than the king. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
